An shirya bikin ne domin ranar 5 ga watan Augusta, a ranar da masu shirya bikin suka ce abin mamaki ne ga Hindu amma kuma hakan na nuna shekara guda tun bayan da majalisar dokokin Indiya ta sake farfado da matsayin wasan kwallon kafa na jiharsa ta Muslim-majority, Jammu da Kashmir.
