Magajin garin Kansas ya yi maraba da taimakon gwamnatin tarayya wajen magance kashe-kashen, amma ya damu da muradin Trump
Magajin garin birnin Kansas Quinton Lucas ya yi tambaya a ranar Lahadi kan dalilin da ya sa Shugaba Trump ya tura jami'an gwamnatin tarayya zuwa biranen Amurka - yana mai cewa yayin da zai yi maraba da taimakon wajen warware kashe-kashen da aka yi a tsakiyar birnin Midwestern, yana ganin matakin zai iya kara zama abin koyi ga Trump.
Lucas, wani dan jam'iyyar Democrat, ya ce a "Fox News Sunday" zanga-zangar da aka yi a baya-bayan nan game da wariyar launin fata da cin zarafin "yan sanda.
"Wannan ba haka ba ne a Kansas City. Mun yi shekara-shekara qara [amma] abin da muke bukatar taimako a kan shi ne a zahiri share wasu daga cikin unsolved kisan."
Lucas ya kara da cewa: "Bari mu yi kokarin sanya da niyya mayar da hankali a kan warware kashe-kashen...Ina ganin idan ka saurari maganganun kwanan nan... muna farin cikin yin aiki tare da jami'an tarayya a iyakance."
Duk da cewa a shirye yake ya yi aiki da jami'an tsaron yankin, Lucas ya ce abin kunya ne ga Trump - musamman dangane da tashe-tashen hankulan da ke kewaye da dabaru da ake amfani da su a Portland, Ore, ta hannun jami'an gwamnatin tarayya - ya sa da yawa daga cikin 'yan majalisar sun nuna damuwa game da kasancewar jami'ai a kan titunan birnin.
"Abin da ba ma bukata shi ne karin man fetur a kan wuta daga jami'an gwamnatin tarayya don yin hakan, ina ganin, wani lamari ne mai ban sha'awa na siyasa", in ji shi.
A ranar Laraba Trump ya sanar da cewa yana tura jami'an tarayya 100 zuwa Chicago don taimakawa wajen yaki da tashe-tashen hankula na wasu laifuka - matakin da ke nuna fadada shiga fadar White House cikin jami'an tsaron gida yayin da Trump ke ci gaba da sanya kansa a matsayin "shari'a da oda".
A ranar Laraba ne "yan bindigar suka kai hari a wani gida da ke birnin Chicago na Amurka, inda suka yi awon gaba da wani mai suna LeGend Taliferro, wanda aka harbe yayin da yake bacci a wani gida da ke birnin Kansas a karshen watan da ya gabata.
Yayin da aika jami'an gwamnatin tarayya don taimakon jami'an tsaron yankin ba a taba ganin irinsa ba - Atoni Janar Bill Barr ya sanar da irin wannan karuwar a watan Disamba ga birane bakwai da suka ga tashin hankali - irin wakilan gwamnatin tarayya da ake aike wa, da kuma wasu dabaru, sun tayar da damuwa a tsakanin "yan majalisar jihohi da na kananan hukumomi.
Wasu 'yan majalisar daga New York zuwa Portland sun yi magana a kan gwamnatin Trump da ta tura jami'an zuwa garuruwan su, musamman bayan rahotannin da ke cewa jami'an gwamnatin tarayya da ba a san ko su wanene ba sun tsare masu zanga-zanga a Portland kuma sun kwashe su a cikin motocin da ba a bayyana ba.
Portland dai ta sha fama da zanga-zangar adawa da cin zarafin 'yan sanda da nuna wariyar launin fata tun bayan mutuwar George Floyd a lokacin da yake tsare a birnin Minneapolis a ranar 25 ga watan Mayu.
