Dole ne a killace matafiya da ke shigowa Birtaniya daga Spain a yanzu na tsawon kwanaki 14, a karkashin sabbin dokokin tafiye-tafiye na coronavirus.
An sanar da su ne a ranar Asabar bayan da aka samu bullar cutar coronavirus a Spain, inda aka samu sabbin kamuwa da cutar sama da 900 a ranar Juma'a.
Jami'an kasar Spain sun kuma yi gargadin cewa za a iya samun tagomashi a yayin da manyan birane suka ga karuwar masu kamuwa da cutar.
Kamfanonin jiragen sama ciki har da British Airways sun soki sabbin matakan da aka dauka a matsayin "soyayya" ga masu hutun Birtaniya.
Mutane a halin yanzu a kan biki a Spain an shawarci ma'aikatar sufuri da ta bi ka'idojin gida, ta koma gida kamar yadda aka saba, kuma ta duba shafin yanar gizon shawarwari na Ofishin Harkokin Waje don ƙarin bayani.
Ofishin harkokin waje yana ba da shawara game da duk amma tafiya mai mahimmanci zuwa babban yankin Spain, duk da haka matakan keɓewa sun shafi waɗanda suka dawo daga Spain, tsibirin Canary da tsibirin Balearic, kamar Majorca da Ibiza.
