WASHINGTON, DC — Sanata Ted Cruz na jihar Texas ya zargi kakakin majalisar wakilai Nancy Pelosi da 'yan jam'iyyar Democrat da tura wani kunshin agajin coronavirus da ke maida hankali kan "mummunan tsabar kudi a matsalar da kuma rufe Amurka" yayinda ake ci gaba da tattaunawa kan matakai na gaba.
A wata hira da ya yi da "Face the Nation" a ranar Lahadi, Cruz ya ce kasar na fuskantar rikice-rikice guda biyu a lokaci guda: annoba ta duniya da ta yi sanadiyyar rayukan mutane fiye da 600,000 a duk duniya da kuma "mummunar bala'in tattalin arziki" a Amurka.
Sai dai Cruz ya ce Pelosi, wanda ya bayyana a kan "Face the Nation" a gaban sanatan, "yana mai da hankali ne a kan wadanda ba su yi hakan ba".
"Manufar 'yan tawayen ita ce ta harba tsabar kudi a kan matsalar da kuma rufe Amurka", in ji dan takarar jam'iyyar Republican ta Texas.
"Kuma musamman, ka dubi $3 tiriliyan doka da ta ke kokarin tura, yana da kawai shoveling kudi ga abokanta, kuma ba a zahiri warware matsalar. Our manufa ya zama Amirkawa so su dawo aiki. Suna so su iya samar wa iyalansu. "
'Yan majalisar dattawa da fadar White House sun shafe makon jiya suna tattaunawa kan sharuddan da suka shafi kashi na hudu na amsar coronavirus, wadanda suke sa ran za su kashe dala tiriliyan daya.
A karshen mako, shugaban ma'aikatan fadar White House Mark Meadows da Sakataren Baitulmalin Amurka Steven Mnuchin sun koma Capitol Hill domin karin tattaunawa da ma'aikatan majalisar dattawa, kuma Mnuchin ya fadawa gidan talbijin na Fox News a wata hira da ya yi a jiya Lahadi cewa, za a bayyana cikakken bayanin da shugaban majalisar dattawa Mitch McConnell ya gabatar a ranar Litinin.
Batun da ya fi jan hankali ga 'yan majalisar - kuma batu ne na takaddama tsakanin 'yan Republican da 'yan Democrat - shi ne batun kara inganta rashin aikin yi, wanda ya fara tafiya a karshen wannan makon.
